      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "5️⃣ Correct comparison (clean interview-ready version)\nWSGI\n\nSync request handling\nOne request per worker\nConcurrency via OS processes\nBlocking I/O\nExample: Django (classic), Flask\n\nASGI\n\nAsync request handling\nMultiple requests per worker\nConcurrency via event loop\nNon-blocking I/O\nExample: FastAPI, Django ASGI\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "5️⃣ Correct comparison (clean interview-ready version)\nWSGI\n\nSync request handling\nOne request per worker\nConcurrency via OS processes\nBlocking I/O\nExample: Django (classic), Flask\n\nASGI\n\nAsync request handling\nMultiple requests per worker\nConcurrency via event loop\nNon-blocking I/O\nExample: FastAPI, Django ASGI\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
