      "versionNonce": 2016141487,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775226369120,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "4️⃣ What WSGI Gives to Django?\nInstead of raw HTTP, Django receives a Python dictionary.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "4️⃣ What WSGI Gives to Django?\nInstead of raw HTTP, Django receives a Python dictionary.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "Xs4W94YkOf1yWu8y_JFDj",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2057.2319108576967,
      "y": 1054.390591593081,
      "width": 429,
      "height": 225,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bEr",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1770223077,
      "version": 245,
      "versionNonce": 1501758913,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775226369120,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "environ = {\n    \"REQUEST_METHOD\": \"GET\",\n    \"PATH_INFO\": \"/products\",\n    \"QUERY_STRING\": \"id=10\",\n}\n\nNow Django can easily process:\nif environ[\"PATH_INFO\"] == \"/products\":\n    return product_view()",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "environ = {\n    \"REQUEST_METHOD\": \"GET\",\n    \"PATH_INFO\": \"/products\",\n    \"QUERY_STRING\": \"id=10\",\n}\n\nNow Django can easily process:\nif environ[\"PATH_INFO\"] == \"/products\":\n    return product_view()",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "tcrxzd5kPMc10x1AF5OWS",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1993.4584733576967,
      "y": 1341.937466593081,
      "width": 275,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bEs",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2041106725,
      "version": 245,
      "versionNonce": 946467535,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775226369120,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "5️⃣ How Response Goes Back\nYour Django view returns:",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "5️⃣ How Response Goes Back\nYour Django view returns:",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "qv53y43I5AV5cULJ4IwfZ",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2047.6381608576967,
      "y": 1408.390591593081,
      "width": 1067,
      "height": 275,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bEt",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 865628741,
      "version": 250,
      "versionNonce": 1367254433,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775226369120,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "return JsonResponse({\"id\": 10, \"name\": \"Phone\"})\nWSGI converts it into HTTP:\n\nHTTP/1.1 200 OK\nContent-Type: application/json\n{\"id\":10,\"name\":\"Phone\"}\n\n✅ Final Interview Line\n\nWSGI is a specification that acts as a bridge between a web server and a Python web application, \nconverting HTTP requests into Python objects and Python responses back into HTTP responses.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "return JsonResponse({\"id\": 10, \"name\": \"Phone\"})\nWSGI converts it into HTTP:\n\nHTTP/1.1 200 OK\nContent-Type: application/json\n{\"id\":10,\"name\":\"Phone\"}\n\n✅ Final Interview Line\n\nWSGI is a specification that acts as a bridge between a web server and a Python web application, \nconverting HTTP requests into Python objects and Python responses back into HTTP responses.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "4SQLaXkPc51XlTTuectL8",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1941.4467546076967,
      "y": 1755.183560343081,
      "width": 506,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bEu",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 272067851,
      "version": 242,
      "versionNonce": 123781359,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775226369120,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "what actually make django as wsgi application?",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "what actually make django as wsgi application?",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "0cwbgMZ21ns3TXxqyhvoy",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1991.1615983576967,
      "y": 1799.906216593081,
      "width": 957,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bEv",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1161623723,
      "version": 243,
      "versionNonce": 750471553,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775226369120,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Django becomes a WSGI application because it exposes a callable named application that \nfollows the WSGI specification.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Django becomes a WSGI application because it exposes a callable named application that \nfollows the WSGI specification.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "TOPN9UAGgkDp1j-pMvWsr",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1993.4740983576967,
      "y": 1896.378872843081,
      "width": 858,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bEw",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 243883435,
      "version": 241,
      "versionNonce": 110676751,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775226369120,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1️⃣ What Makes Any App a WSGI Application?\nA program is a WSGI application if it provides a callable with this signature:",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1️⃣ What Makes Any App a WSGI Application?\nA program is a WSGI application if it provides a callable with this signature:",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "qVw1NVRu50zVOtLw1R6VJ",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2040.0873796076967,
      "y": 1961.710904093081,
      "width": 627,
      "height": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bEx",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 970357771,
      "version": 247,
      "versionNonce": 1685614945,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775226369120,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "application(environ, start_response)\n\nenviron → dictionary containing request data\nstart_response → function used to send status and headers",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "application(environ, start_response)\n\nenviron → dictionary containing request data\nstart_response → function used to send status and headers",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "5-JKm1T5MRLiidto0e9Yi",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1902.1615983576967,
      "y": 2121.355435343081,
      "width": 638,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bEy",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 31511749,
      "version": 242,
      "versionNonce": 311071023,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775226369120,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "in wsgi workers can handle multiple requeest concurrently?",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "in wsgi workers can handle multiple requeest concurrently?",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "q-O0WC0N1CT9zWAySNhaB",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1951.7944108576967,
      "y": 2166.894497843081,
      "width": 1023,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bEz",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1709823077,
      "version": 241,
      "versionNonce": 503684417,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775226369120,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "No. A single WSGI worker usually handles only one request at a time.\nBut the server can run multiple workers, so many requests can still be processed in parallel.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "No. A single WSGI worker usually handles only one request at a time.\nBut the server can run multiple workers, so many requests can still be processed in parallel.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "7kKhLIJGVbIqSWD-lf36x",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1948.6576921076967,
      "y": 2248.460904093081,
      "width": 726,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bF0",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 27043845,
      "version": 247,
      "versionNonce": 1688113999,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775226369120,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1️⃣ Basic WSGI Worker Behavior\nIn traditional WSGI servers like Gunicorn or uWSGI (sync workers):",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1️⃣ Basic WSGI Worker Behavior\nIn traditional WSGI servers like Gunicorn or uWSGI (sync workers):",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "2Keh1YRS5rKgfQ4X8_WJF",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1983.3373796076967,
      "y": 2309.285122843081,
      "width": 781,
      "height": 350,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bF1",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1722403653,
      "version": 334,
      "versionNonce": 683822369,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775226369120,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1 Worker  →  1 Request at a time\nWorker 1 → Request A\nWorker 2 → Request B\nWorker 3 → Request C\n\nEach worker processes its request completely before taking another one.\nSo inside a worker:\nRequest 1 starts\n↓\nRequest 1 finishes\n↓\nRequest 2 starts\n\nNo concurrency inside the worker.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1 Worker  →  1 Request at a time\nWorker 1 → Request A\nWorker 2 → Request B\nWorker 3 → Request C\n\nEach worker processes its request completely before taking another one.\nSo inside a worker:\nRequest 1 starts\n↓\nRequest 1 finishes\n↓\nRequest 2 starts\n\nNo concurrency inside the worker.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "jW_79yDJYMCb5lXbVWmUw",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1939.0053483576967,
      "y": 2693.085904093081,
      "width": 440,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bF2",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 282756197,
      "version": 243,
      "versionNonce": 1965904239,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775226369120,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "2️⃣ How Multiple Requests Are Handled\nConcurrency comes from multiple workers.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "2️⃣ How Multiple Requests Are Handled\nConcurrency comes from multiple workers.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "oS0tdVQoqpyGWROpDVzxE",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1990.8256608576967,
      "y": 2759.117154093081,
      "width": 407,
      "height": 175,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bF3",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1831246155,
      "version": 245,
      "versionNonce": 1008599297,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775226369120,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Gunicorn workers = 4\nWorker1 → Request1\nWorker2 → Request2\nWorker3 → Request3\nWorker4 → Request4\n\nSo 4 requests can run simultaneously.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Gunicorn workers = 4\nWorker1 → Request1\nWorker2 → Request2\nWorker3 → Request3\nWorker4 → Request4\n\nSo 4 requests can run simultaneously.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "q_NSVDqq9jGD8S_YCHhY7",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2060.6850358576967,
      "y": 5114.656216593081,
      "width": 11,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bF4",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 30178117,
      "version": 3,
      "versionNonce": 909518181,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773153374025,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "YZ4aIjGqxeSvomxu3xkZo",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1929.9155046076967,
      "y": 2976.535122843081,
      "width": 407,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bF5",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1348930699,
      "version": 240,
      "versionNonce": 494881679,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775226369120,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "3️⃣ What Happens If a Request Is Slow?",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "3️⃣ What Happens If a Request Is Slow?",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "F750DzbHi1BqnLW5DIqYS",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1974.0912858576967,
      "y": 3017.574185343081,
      "width": 407,
      "height": 275,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bF6",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2116347979,
      "version": 253,
      "versionNonce": 1972910305,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775226369120,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Worker1 → API call taking 5 seconds\nThat worker is blocked for 5 seconds.\nIt cannot process another request.\n\nWorker1 → Busy\nWorker2 → Available\nWorker3 → Available\nWorker4 → Available\n\nIf all workers become busy:\nRequest5 → waits in queue",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Worker1 → API call taking 5 seconds\nThat worker is blocked for 5 seconds.\nIt cannot process another request.\n\nWorker1 → Busy\nWorker2 → Available\nWorker3 → Available\nWorker4 → Available\n\nIf all workers become busy:\nRequest5 → waits in queue",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "ACTdLPOxKbl0C9YDDmOZz",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1919.7865983576967,
      "y": 3333.382779093081,
      "width": 484,
      "height": 75,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bF7",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1889941323,
      "version": 244,
      "versionNonce": 2043478447,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775226369120,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "4️⃣ Why This Happens\nWSGI was designed for synchronous execution.\nThat means the flow is:",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "4️⃣ Why This Happens\nWSGI was designed for synchronous execution.\nThat means the flow is:",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "-8WYj76JYfQS66eCDLsbX",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1572.9506608576967,
      "y": 1531.828091593081,
      "width": 1345.46875,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bF8",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1173464459,
      "version": 26,
      "versionNonce": 1591744485,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773153481591,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
